data.description: One or more photo(s) has been virtually staged. Waterfront home on the Anclote River to hop on your boat or jet ski and be out to the gulf with a pleasant ride! Enjoy this 2 bedroom, 2 bathroom home  that has a split plan, huge family room, bonus room that would make a great home office, and a nice sized fenced yard. This home is at the end of the street, so you only have 1 neighbor. Wonderful location in Historic Tarpon Springs with so much to offer and lots of restaurants and all your shopping needs close by. The Pinellas Trail is a short distance for bike ride or just walk the trail.
